n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | TBA\n| ''[[Lee Bacon#Books|The Last Human]]''<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/phil-lord-chris-miller-sci-fi-project-last-human-spark-bidding-war-1184271|title=Phil Lord, Chris Miller Sci-Fi Project 'Last Human' Sparking Bidding War (Exclusive)|website=The Hollywood Reporter}}</ref>\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" | In development\n|-\n| ''[[The Lego Movie (franchise)#Spin-off films|The Billion Brick Race]]''\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes}}\n|}\n\n==== Acting credits ====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Year\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Title\n! colspan=\"2\" |Role as\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Notes\n|-\n!'''Phil Lord'''\n!'''Christopher Miller'''\n|-\n| 2009\n|''[[Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs (film)|Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs]]''\n|Additional Voices\n|Additional Voices \n| rowspan=\"4\" |Voice roles\n|-\n|2014\n|''[[The Lego Movie]]''\n|{{N/a|None}}\n|TV Presenter\n|-\n| 2018\n|''[[Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse]]''\n|{{N/a|None}} \n|Cop on the radio\n|-\n| 2019\n|''[[The Lego Movie 2: The Second Part]]''\n|{{N/a|None}}\n|Horse / Chocolate Bar / Plantimals / Paper Boy / Chad\n|-\n|TBA\n|''Bucks of America'' \n|{{N/a|None}}\n|Militia Soldier\n|\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" \n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! width=\"65\"| [[Television director|Directors]]\n! width=\"65\"| [[Screenwriting|Writers]]\n! width=\"65\"| [[Television producer|Producers]]\n! Notes\n|-\n| 1999\u20132000\n| ''[[Zoe, Duncan, Jack and Jane]]''\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| Episode: \"Crossing the Line\"\n|-\n| 2000\n| ''[[Go Fish (TV series)|Go Fish]]''\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| Episode: \"Go Wrestling\"\n|-\n| 2002\u20132003\n| ''[[Clone High]]''\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes|Executive}}\n| 13 episodes; also co-creators and supervising directors\n|-\n| 2003\n| ''[[Luis (TV series)|Luis]]''\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes|Supervising}}\n| 5 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|2004\n| ''[[Method & Red]]''\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes|Consulting}}\n| 9 episodes<br>Episodes: \"Well Well Well,\" \"Da Shootout\" and \"A House Apart\" \n|-\n| ''[[Cracking Up (TV series)|Cracking Up]]'' \n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes|Consulting}}\n| 6 episodes\n|-\n| 2005\u20132006\n| ''[[How I Met Your Mother]]''\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| 17 episodes<br>Episodes: \"Sweet Taste of Liberty\" & \"[[Belly Full of Turkey]]\"\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[Brooklyn Nine-Nine]]''\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes|Executive}}\n| Episode: \"Pilot\"\n|-\n| 2015\u20132018\n| ''[[The Last Man on Earth (TV series)|The Last Man on Earth]]''\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes|Executive}}\n| 67 episodes<br>Episodes: \"Alive in Tucson\" & \"The Elephant in the Room\"\n|-\n| 2016\u20132017\n| ''[[Son of Zorn]]''\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes|Executive}}\n| 13 episodes\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Making History (TV series)|Making History]]''\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes|Executive}}\n| 9 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|2017\u2013present\n| ''[[Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs: The Series]]''\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| Executive consultants\n|-\n| ''[[Unikitty!]]''\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes|Executive}}\n|\n|-\n| 2019\u2013present\n| ''[[Bless the Harts]]''\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes|Executive}}\n|\n|}\n\n====Acting credits====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Year\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Title\n! colspan=\"2\" |Role as\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Notes\n|-\n!'''Phil Lord'''\n!'''Christopher Miller'''\n|-\n| 1998\u20131999\n|''[[Caroline in the City]]''\n|Bill\n|Cliff\n| 3 episodes\n|-\n| 2002\u20132003\n|''[[Clone High]]''\n|Principal Dr. Cinnamon J. Scudworth / Genghis Khan\n|JFK /  Vice Principal Mr. Butlertron\n| Voice roles, 13 episodes\n|-\n|2007\n|''[[How I Met Your Mother]]''\n|Too Much Tongue Guy\n|{{n/a|None}}\n|Episode \"How I Met Everyone Else\"\n|-\n| 2020\n|[[Lego Masters (American TV series)|Lego Masters]]\n| Himself\n| Himself\n| Episode \"Movie Genes\"\n|}\n\n==Recurring (acting) collaborators==\nThe following contains a list of recurring actors in films and TV shows directed, produced, and/or wrote by Lord and Miller.\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-  style=\"background:#b0c4de; text-align:center;\"\n! \n! ''[[Clone High]]''\n! ''[[Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs (film)|Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs]]''\n! ''[[21 Jump Street (film)|21 Jump Street]]''\n! ''[[Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs 2]]''\n! ''[[The Lego Movie]]''\n! ''[[22 Jump Street]]''\n! ''[[The Last Man on Earth (TV series)|The Last Man on Earth]]''\n! ''[[Son of Zorn]]''\n! ''[[Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse]]''\n! ''[[The Lego Movie 2: The Second Part]]''\n|-\n|[[Will Forte]]\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}}\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}}\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}}\n|-\n| [[Bill Hader]]\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}}\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n| [[Anna Faris]]\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}}\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n| [[Jake Johnson]]\n|\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|  \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|\n|\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}}\n|\n|-\n| [[Jonah Hill]]\n|\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|  \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}}\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}}\n|\n|\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|-\n| [[Nick Offerman]]\n|\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|  \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}}\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}}\n|\n|\n| \n| style=\"text-alig