|''[[Caroline in the City]]''\n|Bill\n|Cliff\n| 3 episodes\n|-\n| 2002\u20132003\n|''[[Clone High]]''\n|Principal Dr. Cinnamon J. Scudworth / Genghis Khan\n|JFK /  Vice Principal Mr. Butlertron\n| Voice roles, 13 episodes\n|-\n|2007\n|''[[How I Met Your Mother]]''\n|Too Much Tongue Guy\n|{{n/a|None}}\n|Episode \"How I Met Everyone Else\"\n|-\n| 2020\n|[[Lego Masters]]\n| Himself\n| Himself\n| Episode \"Movie Genes\"\n|}\n\n==Recurring (acting) collaborators==\nThe following contains a list of recurring actors in films and TV shows directed, produced, and/or wrote by Lord and Miller.\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-  style=\"background:#b0c4de; text-align:center;\"\n! \n! ''[[Clone High]]''\n! ''[[Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs (film)|Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs]]''\n! ''[[21 Jump Street (film)|21 Jump Street]]''\n! ''[[Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs 2]]''\n! ''[[The Lego Movie]]''\n! ''[[22 Jump Street]]''\n! ''[[The Last Man on Earth (TV series)|The Last Man on Earth]]''\n! ''[[Son of Zorn]]''\n! ''[[Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse]]''\n! ''[[The Lego Movie 2: The Second Part]]''\n|-\n|[[Will Forte]]\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}}\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}}\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}}\n|-\n| [[Bill Hader]]\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}}\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n| [[Anna Faris]]\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}}\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n| [[Jake Johnson]]\n|\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|  \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{X mark}} \n|\n|\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\