)|Communist Party]]||63,601||3.6||4||\u20133\n|-\n|align=left|[[Communist Party of Sweden (1924)|Communist Party (H\u00f6glund Tendency)]]||26,301||1.5||1||New\n|-\n|align=left|Other parties||84||0.0||0||0\n|-\n|align=left|Invalid/blank votes||5,473||\u2013||\u2013||\u2013\n|-\n|align=left|Valid votes||1,765,586||\u2013||\u2013||\u2013\n|-\n|align=left|'''Total'''||'''1,771,059'''||'''100'''||'''230'''||'''0'''\n|-\n|align=left|Registered voters/turnout||3,338,892||53.0||\u2013||\u2013\n|-\n|align=left colspan=5|Source: Nohlen & St\u00f6ver\n|}\n{{Bar box\n|title=Popular vote\n|titlebar=#ddd\n|width=600px\n|barwidth=350px\n|bars=\n{{Bar percent|S|{{Swedish Social Democratic Party/meta/color}}|41.09}}\n{{Bar percent|AV|{{Moderate Party/meta/color}}|26.12}}\n{{Bar percent|FL|{{Liberals (Sweden)/meta/color}}|12.97}}\n{{Bar percent|B|{{Centre Party (Sweden)/meta/color}}|10.78}}\n{{Bar percent|LP|#33C7FF|3.94}}\n{{Bar percent|SKP (Comintern)|{{Left Party (Sweden)/meta/color}}|3.59}}\n{{Bar percent|SKP (non-Comintern)|#611c21|1.49}}\n{{Bar percent|Others|{{Other/meta/color}}|0.00}}\n}}\n{{Bar box\n|title=Parliament seats\n|titlebar=#ddd\n|width=600px\n|barwidth=350px\n|bars=\n{{Bar percent|S|{{Swedish Social Democratic Party/meta/color}}|45.22}}\n{{Bar percent|AV|{{Moderate Party/meta/color}}|28.26}}\n{{Bar percent|FL|{{Liberals (Sweden)/meta/color}}|12.61}}\n{{Bar percent|B|{{Centre Party (Sweden)/meta/color}}|10.00}}\n{{Bar percent|LP|#33C7FF|1.74}}\n{{Bar percent|SKP (Comintern)|{{Left Party (Sweden)/meta/color}}|1.74}}\n{{Bar percent|SKP (non-Comintern)|#611c21|0.43}}\n}}\n\n==Constituency results==\n\n===Percentage share===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=text-align:right\n!Location\n!Land\n!Share\n!Votes\n![[Social Democrats (Sweden)|S]]\n![[Moderate Party (Sweden)|AV]]\n![[Free-minded National Association|FL]]\n![[Centre Party (Sweden)|B]]\n![[Liberal Party of Sweden|LP]]\n![[Left Party (Sweden)|K]]\n![[Communist Party of Sweden (1924)|KP]]\n!Other\n!Left\n!